      I am a 21-year old who enjoys developing web apps that are a joy to use,
      following best practices and writing clean and maintainable code.
    </p>

    <ul
      class="text-lg sm:text-xl col-span-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 sm:gap-7 md:gap-8 lg:mt-10 lg:justify-center"
